<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/234">أَبُو بَكْرٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4290">أَبِي حَصِينٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2343">سَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> <span class="c2">«﴿وَجَعَلْنَاكُمْ شُعُوبًا وَقَبَائِلَ﴾ قَالَ الشُّعُوبُ الْقَبَائِلُ الْعِظَامُ وَالْقَبَائِلُ الْبُطُونُ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>